{"tid":2302181,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"廠商們快給MAMAMOO華莎多點贊助或者簽約！看完就想跟著她買買買","createTime":"2020-11-27T02:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T16:29:18.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"94a75de3f5a4b6e091c1615433ef7862a170bf2b","tid":2302181,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T02:29:52.000Z","msg":"MAMAMOO華莎雖然不是愛豆中最美的，但一定是最會穿衣服的女愛豆之一。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一向百變的穿衣風格是華莎最大的，加上自信魅力，使得她在以白瘦為美的K-POP圈殺出了一條另類血路。 大膽、前衛的HIPHOP風在她的加持下也逐漸變成了女孩們爭相模仿的Look。<br />\n<br />\n華莎的另一大魔力就在於無論穿什麼，似乎都能打造出獨特的氣質和魅力，任何一個大牌在她身上既是點綴，也是與她相呼應的主角，完全不互搶鏡頭。 華莎的時尚消化能力有多強呢？ 今天我們就來看一看~在大家的印象中L牌似乎和HIPHOP風風馬牛不相及，但華莎就不這樣想了。 寬鬆的運動褲配上高腰短褲，再搭上露腰緊身衣，就站在普通住宅樓的頂層，映襯著灰色磚瓦，不經意間就拍出了一組時尚大片。 有錢人專屬的L牌似乎突然變得平易近人了~<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e48e7bd6466f79484a22e762d8ba9a55/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131897-886350.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e48e7bd6466f79484a22e762d8ba9a55%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131897-886350.jpg&h=f0763cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_b5ec6ea7906fcfc41d757e1c7f3f4807/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131897-886352.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_b5ec6ea7906fcfc41d757e1c7f3f4807%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131897-886352.jpg&h=31f50be4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_2eaab269527deef3c1e084e1f4e69199/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131897-886353.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_2eaab269527deef3c1e084e1f4e69199%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131897-886353.jpg&h=def71dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n運動風和華莎一直都很搭，被子一樣的外套看上去平淡無奇，但為什麼穿在她身上就立刻顯得時髦了100倍呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_4fe3284a6ae24f371ec2ea6c970dc356/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131897-886354.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_4fe3284a6ae24f371ec2ea6c970dc356%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131897-886354.jpg&h=bfa0db38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_edb32716e12206518ac7ed74efdaaae1/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131897-886355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_edb32716e12206518ac7ed74efdaaae1%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131897-886355.jpg&h=1d1d8610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d925d25a6e9f14ab62cf79ee306ef900/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131897-886356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d925d25a6e9f14ab62cf79ee306ef900%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131897-886356.jpg&h=9d7f651e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可甜可鹽的華莎穿上裙子也自帶一種禦姐的氣質，腰包和肩下包的搭配估計又要颳起一陣時尚大風了。 ALL BLACK LOOK一直都是氣場的象徵，禦姐的ALL BLACK LOOK有種要衝破銀幕的霸氣。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_54abe46b0742e6c1a01afd40016e46af/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131897-886357.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_54abe46b0742e6c1a01afd40016e46af%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131897-886357.jpg&h=b292ccdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_e8469a7510eea1908b5db8778f3ce1b7/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-11-26/131897-886358.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_e8469a7510eea1908b5db8778f3ce1b7%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-11-26%2F131897-886358.jpg&h=b74505a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n看完了華莎的各類時尚演繹，只想說品牌商們，快點給她打錢，看完華莎的穿搭，每一件都想買。<br />\n<br />\n「圖：華莎IG」"},{"pid":"3358bfaf6e32cc2ab910494af968debc66de6c58","tid":2302181,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-27T0